def shirt_in_location(location:item):
    # Check if theres a shirt in the specified location
    symbol has_shirt=exists shirt: item : is_clothes_shirt(shirt) and inside(shirt, location)
    return has_shirt

behavior locate_shirt():
    body:
        # If there is a shirt in the current known locations, go directly to it
        if exists drawer: item : is_closetdrawer(drawer) and shirt_in_location(drawer):
            bind drawer: item where:
                is_closetdrawer(drawer) and shirt_in_location(drawer)
            achieve close_char(char, drawer)

        # Otherwise, search in all unvisited closet drawers
        else:
            foreach drawer: item:
                if is_closetdrawer(drawer) and not visited(drawer):
                    observe(drawer, "Check if there is a shirt in the drawer")
                    
behavior __goal__():
    body:
        locate_shirt()
